<!--  ABOUT                                                      -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div style="background:#1a1a2e; border:1px solid #3a3a5c; border-radius:6px; padding:1em 1.4em; margin-bottom:1.2em;">
== About ==
Cybots is a game of strategy played where you, the Controller, must purchase and then configure a range of Cybernetic Warrior Bots in readiness for battle. A game of Cybots is played over a set period of time. Check the '''Time Till Reset''' on the sidebar menu for how much time is remaining before the game restarts. During this time period all Controllers compete to obtain the most '''Battle Experience Points (Exp)'''. Battle Experience is earnt only by achieving victory in combat. At any point in time you can check the top scoring Controllers using the '''Scoreboard''' (also located in the side bar).

To win battles and survive the Outlands you must configure your bots using a range of equipment options purchased using a limited amount of cash.

However you won't win just by having tons of cash — in the end the winner is decided by Battle Exp. In other words, cash is the means by which you can compete, but in the end it's how well your bots do in battle that counts.
</div>

